{"tid":2450902,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"突發！旺角一男子被拳棍圍毆 再被捉上車擄走","createTime":"2021-03-17T17:34:01.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-17T17:54:21.000Z","uid":391580,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"1ab3ad841230069d418072571b862fbe863bdf5a","tid":2450902,"uid":391580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T17:34:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0fFw0zc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0fFw0zc.jpg&h=0b23cca4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"228244b3a1b365ecf9aa16b9760ccde7d0ac51ef","tid":2450902,"uid":26773,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T17:34:45.000Z","msg":"有車牌都搵唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f179b7d9307f5e37bebc83583a569c7ff9696781","tid":2450902,"uid":79793,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T17:35:14.000Z","msg":"聽日睇新聞咪又係差佬拉人<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55d81fdf45f55deb5c10583a408a2cfcc8a89b44","tid":2450902,"uid":391580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T17:35:26.000Z","msg":"網上流傳一條大約40秒的短片，可見有3輛私家車及七人車停在馬路上，多名大漢則將一名男子用力推向其中一輛七人車，該名男子似乎赤裸上身，被多人拳打面部及起腳踢。旁邊則有人負責把風。<br />\n<br />\n片段可見，該名男子曾一度嘗試掙脫，但仍未逃離已被眾人再次圍毆，男子狀似求饒，但對方卻亮出棍棒不停打向該名男子。最終，該名男子被人推上七人車後，開車絕塵而去。<br />\n<br />\n該片段相信是在行人天橋高位向對落的馬路拍攝，負責拍片的女子，曾在片段中透露過報警，並對於拍下片段感到憂心，恐該批大漢發現她拍片，及怕會被對方打傷。"},{"pid":"4475c9e42722353731950665a81ee8e483ecf514","tid":2450902,"uid":2300,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"228244b3a1b365ecf9aa16b9760ccde7d0ac51ef","tid":2450902,"uid":26773,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T17:34:45.000Z","msg":"有車牌都搵唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T17:35:57.000Z","msg":"傻啦，點會搵自己人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37778313deaa3f8b661bfde2fe4dcaf444b6f522","tid":2450902,"u